  "texts": [
    "With the increasing reliance on information technology, the importance of cyber range exercises in security training is highlighted.",
    "Traditional methods often suffer from the overuse of limited scenarios, which can reduce educational impact due to predictability and information leakage.",
    "CyExec* overcomes these challenges by providing diverse, randomized scenarios that maintain the same learning objectives, enhancing teaching effectiveness and mitigating the risk of cheating.",
    "Compared to VM-based systems, CyExec* demonstrates significant improvements in resource efficiency, using less memory, CPU, and storage, thus enabling more complex scenarios to be run simul-taneously.",
    "This paper has described the architecture and effectiveness of CyExec*, comparing it to existing platforms, and discusses future enhancements aimed at enriching scenario variety, online exercise application, and evaluating educational impact.M."
